a lot of the time, i like to lay in bed forever untill my boyfriend wakes me up with a morning bowl and we hang out with eachother untill i go take a shower and get ready for my day...but i could be at work before 9am also, so you never knowwwww.

Well, everything seems to be alright now a days. Hopefully, it won't change. I think just being moody made me act all upset and stupid crap. I realy can't explain it, but Nikki said it pretty clear in a post below this one. So lately, all I have been focusing on is my job and getting as many hours as I can, because my rent is $375 a month, and I got to pay my phone bill on top of that also; I know I can afford it, but I need to save my tips for food, toiletries, etc..This time, I'm going to be prepared when I move, unlike the LAST time, when I kind of got thrown into the whole thing, and I got screwed over in the end. That won't happen again. Also, I think I'm going to focus on my weight thing. Being 160 is not something I want to be anymore...I know I have a lot of muscle, but I want to have a firm tummy. *KISS* to my man and all my good friends in my life. <3
I can not understand why everything is so upsetting to me lately... Right now my life sucks. I need to get the hell out of here ASAP. Ugh...

Yeah so I got lazy and forgot what my old password was...so that is why I havent updated in awhile. Anywho, I dont feel good and I have no life. my best friend's 21st is Thursday. Im going to go drink my sorrows away because I cant stand my Bf. he is tearing me apart and Im tired of it. Blah, enough of my rambling...heres a new poem I wrote not to long ago: Feelings too many thoughts going through my mind are you really the one for me, or was i just being blind... by lust; you had me for months i dont know if this is working for me.. do you even give a damn about how i feel or is flaking some sort of new deal? saying one thing to me, then doing a fucking other? im not going to deal with this bullshit any longer. im sick and tired of being the "good girlfriend" im going to rebel sooner or later if shit doesnt come to an end. you better see how it effects me in one way or another because if you dont change your ways, im going to go find me another lover. so take this little poem into consideration because if you dont, our relationship will be a total obliteration. And Of COURSE, it is to my bf. I miss you guys who are on here...<3

you all need to get lives and try to at least unglue yourselves from the PC.

the others...well if you have a life outside this three diminsonial box, then so be it. I love you too because you dont rest your lives around fucking ignorant people on a computer.

+_Untitled_+

Nowhere to go, Nowhere to hide...
Massichistic feelings start to appear inside...
My mind is racing with fear of rejection
Heart over soul is like the feelings of tension...I get when your presence is near
But only when I see you, I start yo lose my fear...of pain that I could sense in the air
Whenever you walked passed me and just stared.

How do I go about his.
Why can't you just see.
My heart is racing for you, like a crackhead on speed.
My life is a waste, I don't know why...
I feel the way I do inside
But all I know is I'm going to try...
To have you in my arms for just one night...
To hold you there and never let go,
And tell you everything that you want to know


Nobody.

Nobody knows.
Nobody cares.
Mixed up emotions turn from smoldering
to flare.
My head's gone mad
The fibers are unraveled and
My heart is fluttering so bad.
Killing me inside..slowly.
Nobody knows.
Nobody cares.
Killer instincts...twisted thoughts
Suicidal tendancies..no memories lost.
Murderous...scandalous...FUCKED UP
Individual.
Nobody knows.
Nobody cares.
